{"type":"message","id":"9d3b5d52","parentId":"9ea68fce","timestamp":"2026-02-15T15:11:23.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Reviewing Recent Progress**\n\nI've successfully pushed the updates, and the commit hash is `4c8dec21`. I've finished setting up the CI/CD workflow, including linting, testing with a matrix, and security checks. I've also created the Dependabot configuration for daily updates. Everything seems to be running smoothly so far.\n\n\n**Concluding Project Tasks**\n\nI've completed the remaining tasks, including rewriting the `README.md` to include badges and a contribution section, as well as establishing the Docker publish workflow to GHCR. All Git commands have been successfully executed, and I'm ready to report the final status.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"## Mission Complete\n\nI have successfully implemented the GitHub Automation & Guardian protocols.\n\n### 1. Automation Infrastructure (`.github/`)\n*   **CI/CD Pipeline (`ci-cd.yml`):**\n    *   **Linting:** `flake8` checks for syntax errors and code quality.\n    *   **Testing:** Matrix build running `pytest` on **Python 3.11** and **3.14-dev**.\n    *   **Security:** integrated **CodeQL** analysis for vulnerability scanning.\n    *   **Trigger:** Activates on pushes/PRs to `main` and `dev`.\n*   **Dependabot (`dependabot.yml`):** Configured for **daily** updates on `pip` and `github-actions` dependencies.\n*   **Container Registry (`docker-publish.yml`):**\n    *   Automated Docker builds triggered by release publication or tag push.\n    *   Publishes directly to **GHCR** (`ghcr.io/Dykij/DMarket-Telegram-Bot`).\n\n### 2. Documentation (`README.md`)\n*   **Status Badges:** Added dynamic shields for **CI Status**, **Python Version**, and **License**.\n*   **AI Contribution:** Added a specialized \"How to Contribute (AI Agents)\" section referencing the knowledge base.\n\n### 3. Execution Status\n*   **Branch:** `dev`\n*   **Commit Hash:** `4c8dec21`\n*   **Message:** \"Chore: GitHub Automation (Actions, Dependabot, GHCR)\"\n\nThe repository is now fully automated and ready for dual-brain collaboration.","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":9883,"output":479,"cacheRead":8686,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10362,"cost":{"input":0.019766,"output":0.0057480000000000005,"cacheRead":0.0017372000000000002,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0272512}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771168276007}}
